text: Furze Hill is a hamlet in Hampshire, England. Furze Hill or Furzehill may also refer to: *Furzehill, a hamlet in Devon, England *Furzehills, a hamlet in Lincolnshire, England *Furze Hill SSSI, a Site of Special Scientific Interest in Cambridgeshire, England *Furzehill Wood, in Dorset, England *Furzehill Plantation, in Devon, England
title: Furze Hill (disambiguation)
